{"tid":2184083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"管有攻擊性武器案兩警連番錯漏 無記錄檢取雷射筆 錯寫與案無關證物","createTime":"2020-09-01T10:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T11:37:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c99e9c1742f76b7307785f687f4b345518c744c5","tid":2184083,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/XSBJTHTPHJCLVIPCV2ZVN3ZVQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FXSBJTHTPHJCLVIPCV2ZVN3ZVQY%2F&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=cee73655\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FXSBJTHTPHJCLVIPCV2ZVN3ZVQY%2F&h=3b585948\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/XSBJTHTPHJCLVIPCV2ZVN3ZVQY/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年11月市民悼念墮樓身亡的科大生周梓樂，有女籌款員在黃大仙廟附近被截查搜出士巴拿及雷射筆，被控管有攻擊性武器罪，案件今開審。辯方爭議警方處理證物鏈有問題，審訊中途揭發證物警員兩大失誤，包括在口供紙沒提過檢取雷射筆，並將檢取證物事宜記錄在私人記事簿上，沒在警察記事冊披露，連主控官及調查主管都不知情。控方申請在審訊中途將警員私人記事本呈堂，裁判官卻認為記事本出處不明，多番質疑主控不懂法律原則，「點解我（官）依家好似教緊書咁嘅喂？」"},{"pid":"1823a9c3141aaa1495d6120ededcc6f6c9e1f3f7","tid":2184083,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:25:47.000Z","msg":"控方下午撤回將警員私人記事簿呈堂的申請，並傳召另一名處理證物的偵緝警員張錦志作供。張稱被告被捕當日接手案件，將雷射筆等證物放在辦公室一個櫃內，有鎖匙上鎖，全警署只有他擁有該櫃鎖匙。<br />\n<br />\n他在辯方盤問下承認，收到涉案證物後並無將資料輸入電腦系統，櫃中的證物進出亦無紀錄。辯方直指張違反警例，張承認「依家諗返係」，但不同意自己是疏忽或蓄意違規。"},{"pid":"86430e341cf1a9d0cafef503dc1532fdb05ae417","tid":2184083,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b2794a2a30af7ce401d63feb3b63053a3ba688","tid":2184083,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:28:37.000Z","msg":"弱智毅進狗唔識字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4af6ec5904aa65a1a1cdd2c89ff4edcd6e36129","tid":2184083,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"黨媒truth hk又出fake news 又用721微博假圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2183510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2183510</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6b1c6201a5bb36637843ebac1122853048a82d04","tid":2184083,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86430e341cf1a9d0cafef503dc1532fdb05ae417","tid":2184083,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:30:43.000Z","msg":"<